'''绿巧言虫'''（學名：{{lang|la|'''''Eulalia viridis'''''}}）是[[葉鬚蟲目|葉鬚蟲目]][[葉鬚蟲科|葉鬚蟲科]][[巧言蟲屬|巧言蟲屬]]之下的一個[[多毛纲|多毛纲]]物種<ref name="COL" />，有着亮綠色的外表。本物種長約{{convert|5|to|15|cm|in|0|abbr=on}}。在[[北大西洋|北大西洋]]海域，見於[[歐洲|歐洲]]的[[挪威|挪威]]、[[英國|英國]]及[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]<ref name='id10360' />的淺海或[[無孔貽貝|貽貝床]]<ref name="Brusca2003" /><ref name="Hayward1995" />。

其[[种加词|种加词]]“''viridis''”意为“绿色的”。

== 形態描述 ==
巧言蟲是一種背部扁平又纖細的蠕蟲，有體節高達200節。蠕蟲最長可以生長至{{convert|15|cm|in|0|abbr=on}}，顏色從中綠色到亮綠色。頭部有五條觸角、兩隻眼及四對tentacular cirri；the eversible proboscis is cylindrical and dotted with rounded papillae. Each body segment has a pair of {{tsl|en|Parapodium||parapodia}}, and the {{tsl|en|Cirrus (biology)||cirri}} on these are long, thin and pointed. They project outwards, forming a fringe down each side of the body.<ref name=MarLIN>{{cite web |url=http://www.marlin.ac.uk/species/detail/1515 |title=Green-leaf worm: ''Eulalia viridis'' |author=Pizzolla, P.F. |year=2008 |work=MarLIN |publisher=Plymouth: Marine Biological Associat的ion |accessdate=23 July 2017 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119214354/https://www.marlin.ac.uk/species/detail/1515 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 分佈及棲息地 ==
1990年代以前，巧言蟲被認為遍佈東北大西洋，包括環繞英國的水域<ref name='id10360' />，但形態學及生物化學研究表明在分佈於南部的物種應屬另一物種，即''{{tsl|en|Eulalia clavigera}}''；而這兩個物種形成了一個[[複合種|生物複合種]]<ref name="Fish2011" />。

在[[北大西洋|北大西洋]]海域，見於[[歐洲|歐洲]]的[[挪威|挪威]]、[[英國|英國]]及[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]

As now recognised, ''E. viridis'' is native to the northeastern Atlantic Ocean where it is found in the waters off Norway, Sweden, Denmark and Germany, as well as the <!-- [[Faroe_Islands|Faroe Islands]] -->[[法罗群岛|法罗群岛]], Iceland and <!-- [[Disko_Island|Disko Island]] -->[[迪斯科岛|迪斯科岛]] at depths from the mid-shore down to about {{convert|150|m|ft|-2|abbr=on}}. It is typically found on rocky coasts and on shelly gravel,<ref name=MSIP>{{cite web |url=http://species-identification.org/species.php?species_group=macrobenthos_polychaeta&menuentry=soorten&id=548&tab=beschrijving |title=''Eulalia viridis'' |author=de Kluijver, M.J. |work=Macrobenthos of the North Sea – Polychaeta |publisher=Marine Species Identification Portal |accessdate=23 July 2017 |archive-date=2021-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209103252/http://species-identification.org/species.php?species_group=macrobenthos_polychaeta&menuentry=soorten&id=548&tab=beschrijving |dead-url=no }}</ref> in rock crevices and <!-- [[mussel|mussel]] -->[[無孔貽貝|無孔貽貝]] beds.<ref name=MarLIN/>

主要分佈於在[[中國|中國]]分佈於[[山東半島|山東半島]]、[[遼東半島|遼東半島]]<ref name=csdb /><ref name=ChenYi />、[[黄海|黄海]]、[[东海|东海]]、[[南中國海|南中國海]]<ref name='id10360'/>，還有[[白海|白海]]、[[新西伯利亞群岛|新西伯利亞群岛]]、[[白令海|白令海]]、[[千岛群岛|千岛群岛]]、[[勘察加半岛|勘察加半岛]]、[[鄂霍次克海|鄂霍次克海]]、[[日本海|日本海]]等海域<ref name='id10360'/>。
一般栖息于北方和亚热带水域以及主要栖息于[[潮间带|潮间带]]和[[潮下带|潮下带]][[海藻|海藻]]、[[藤壶|藤壶]]、[[牡蛎|牡蛎]]及[[海鞘|海鞘]]等附着动物和岩石下<ref name='id10360'/><ref name=Brusca2003 /><ref name=Hayward1995 />。其生存的海拔下限为-2400米<ref name='id10360'/>。

== 生物學 ==
Although many worms in this family are <!-- [[Predation|predators]] -->[[捕食|捕食]] and actively hunt prey, ''E. viridis'' seems to be more selective in its diet, and researchers found that it only consumed moribund or dead animal tissue. Breeding does not take place until the worms are at least two years old, and they are not thought to form swarms as do some other related species.<ref name=Study/> The greenish gelatinous egg mass is attached to <!-- [[brown_algae|brown algae]] -->[[褐藻纲|褐藻纲]], but some populations seem not to have egg masses. The larvae pass through one or two <!-- [[trochophore|trochophore]] -->[[担轮幼虫|担轮幼虫]] stages and two other stages before settling on the sea bed as a five- to nine-segmented larva, after up to nine weeks.<ref name=Study>{{cite book |author=Australian Biological Resources Study |title=Polychaetes & Allies: The Southern Synthesis |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Rin4l7QZ1YEC&pg=PA145 |year=2000 |publisher=Csiro Publishing |isbn=978-0-643-06571-0 |pages=145–147 |access-date=2021-12-09 |archive-date=2021-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206070849/https://books.google.com/books?id=Rin4l7QZ1YEC&pg=PA145 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

